      <title>印尼呼吁中国帮助缓和中东紧张局势</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-18/indonesia-sees-china-using-influence-to-cool-middle-east-tension</link>
      <description><![CDATA[印度尼西亚外交部长王毅在访问印度尼西亚期间敦促中国利用其影响力防止中东紧张局势升级。王毅在北京旨在深化与雅加达的外交关系之际访问了该群岛。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-18/indonesia-sees-china-using-influence-to-cool-middle-east-tension</guid>
