      <title>拜登称中国“仇外”，加剧2024年竞选言辞</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-17/biden-calls-china-xenophobic-ramping-up-campaign-rhetoric</link>
      <description><![CDATA[乔·拜登总统在摇摆州宾夕法尼亚州的竞选活动中，称中国为“仇外者”，同时强调了这个亚洲国家的经济困境，试图证明美国的经济实力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-17/biden-calls-china-xenophobic-ramping-up-campaign-rhetoric</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 17 Apr 2024 20:55:16 GMT</pubDate>
